<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06038b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06038b">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06038b"> 38(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> day of hostages</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[lines from James Clarence Mangan&apos;s poem &lsquo;Lament for the Princes of Tyrone and Tyrconnell&rsquo;]</font> &mdash; <br> <br>If one <mark>the Day of Hostages</mark> <br>The fruit had from the parent bough <br>Been rudely torn <br>In sight of Munster&apos;s bands&mdash;MacNee&apos;s&mdash; <br>Such flow the blood of Conn, I trow, could ill have borne. <small> W.B. Yeats, <a name="YEATS" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#YEATS"><cite title="source">A Book of Irish Verse</cite></a> (1900) 37</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
